---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutpfp from "../assets/about-me1.png";
---

<section id="about" class="max-w-425 m-auto sm:-scroll-mt-5 lg:scroll-mt-5 sm:mt-15">

  <h3 class="text-3xl text-center text-white font-bold pt-20 pb-5 sm:pb-0 md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl lg:hidden">So, who am I?</h3>

  <div class="about-container flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-white p-8  lg:flex-row-reverse sm:pt-8 lg:justify-around">

      <div class="about-img-container flex items-center justify-center sm:w-2/3 sm:max-w-105 md:max-w-120 lg:max-w-150">
          <Image src={aboutpfp} alt="About me picture" class="rounded-md object-cover w-64 h-64 sm:w-full sm:h-auto" />
      </div>

      <div class="about-text-container text-center pt-8 sm:p-6 sm:flex-2 sm:pl-8 sm:text-left md:text-lg lg:text-xl md:space-y-5">
          <h3 class="text-3xl text-center text-white font-bold pb-5 md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl hidden lg:flex">So, who am I?</h3>
          <p>
              I'm currently studying Systems Engineering at UTN (Universidad Tecnológica Nacional) in Buenos Aires. I hold a B2 English certificate from AACI, having completed 6 years of study.
              <br><br>
              I've been designing web pages with passion since I was 14, learning from videos, documentation and practising, always trying to improve. As you could see, I have some projects that I've developed to show what I'm able to do as a freelancer front end developer.
              <br><br>
              I really enjoy making web pages, and I hope to create yours!
          </p>
        
       </div>
    
  </div>
</section>
